Head. Antennae 0.45−0.47 times as long as body. Antennal segments ratio as I: II: III: IV = 1: 1.88−2.09: 1.76−1.91: 2.18−2.47. Distal part of Ant. IV with many smooth sensory chaetae, normal ciliate chaetae, a pin chaeta and a bilobed apical bulb (
